Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.76,0:00:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當月光照射黑夜之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.47,0:00:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳說 促使宇宙舞動著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.44,0:00:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在禁忌的決鬥展開時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.31,0:00:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死神正自遙遠的地方 呼喊著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.92,0:00:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(超重神)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.76,0:00:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罪惡為此而戴上了面具\N希望能以此錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.53,0:00:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換取持續戮力不停\N所追求的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.54,0:00:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為命運而不知所措之\N嘆息的玫瑰念珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.34,0:00:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因無法抹去的記憶\N而為愛顫抖著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.29,0:00:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當月光照亮黑夜之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.99,0:01:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳說促使得宇宙舞動著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.09,0:01:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虛幻的墜天使們啊\N美麗的飛翔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.07,0:01:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在禁忌的決鬥展開時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.84,0:01:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死神正自遙遠的地方呼喊著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.66,0:01:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.23,0:01:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾有個好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.54,0:01:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.31,0:01:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等檢查完畢機械週邊後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.98,0:01:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就去修理動力傳達系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.58,0:01:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.41,0:01:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去進行控制系統的檢測
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.95,0:02:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.82,0:02:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動作更靈敏一點\N靈敏一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.02,0:02:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.46,0:02:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的移動船塢好可憐喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.89,0:02:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就把你修好\N等我一下哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.96,0:02:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,班長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.69,0:02:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要檢測控制系統的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.23,0:02:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就必須先解除\N系統的防護才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.20,0:02:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.60,0:02:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要小心\N不要讓敵人從外部趁虛而入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.20,0:02:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.04,0:02:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那邊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.00,0:02:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫你們動作快一點嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.94,0:02:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她長得既漂亮人又聰明\N而且重感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.75,0:02:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是個很有氣質的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.58,0:02:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會崇拜她也是因為這個原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.26,0:02:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城內受損的程度\N比想像的還要輕微
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.83,0:02:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五天之內就可以復原了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.83,0:02:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有硬體設備受損吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.53,0:02:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.90,0:02:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女僕們及G戰騎都沒有任何傷亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.61,0:02:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司的復原情況也很順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.71,0:02:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.44,0:03:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.94,0:03:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前那件事情怎麼樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.21,0:03:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經著手進行整理了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.36,0:03:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 有一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.79,0:03:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她卻突然消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.29,0:03:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像煙霧般在眾人之前消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.03,0:03:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿她的存在\N打從一開始就是個幻覺似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.11,0:03:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的名字叫做紅綾香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.88,0:03:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我一位消失了的摯友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.02,0:03:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第九話遙遠的擁抱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.22,0:03:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.49,0:03:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是幹什麼呀 妳們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.12,0:03:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老是這樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.69,0:03:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經好了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.23,0:03:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們看 這麼有精神...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.83,0:03:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以妳們快放了我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.57,0:03:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.13,0:03:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得要好好的接受\N精密檢查才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.64,0:04:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蝶雪拉、瑪莉妮雅\N壓住他的手腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.84,0:04:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要亂動啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.34,0:04:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不乖一點就打你屁屁哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.28,0:04:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶 我也想看看\N英司少爺脫光光的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.08,0:04:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會頭痛、噁心想吐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.28,0:04:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 要檢查了 脫掉\N哇~混蛋住手..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.32,0:04:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要脫啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.56,0:04:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們統統給我記住!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.99,0:04:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊~吵死了 吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.90,0:04:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是鬆了一口氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.90,0:04:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛回來的時候\N看起來好像快死掉了一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.54,0:04:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.57,0:04:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何 自己操作的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.14,0:04:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就知道一直都在操控\N超重皇的斗牙有多厲害了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.38,0:04:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那玩意哪有什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.95,0:04:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要習慣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.91,0:04:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一樣可以馬上控制的得心應手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.95,0:04:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呀~都忘了是斗牙的建議\N你才好不容易能贏的耶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.42,0:04:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.45,0:04:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過英司好厲害喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.52,0:04:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次坐上超重皇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.36,0:04:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以有不錯的戰鬥表現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.26,0:04:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧~對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.46,0:05:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定懂的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.16,0:05:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要說會讓他得意忘形的話啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.97,0:05:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這是事實嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.60,0:05:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.15,0:05:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.55,0:05:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.06,0:05:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是受夠妳們了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.46,0:05:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白痴迷糊護士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.39,0:05:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爺等一等啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.93,0:05:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有檢查完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.27,0:05:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們什麼都沒看到啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.24,0:05:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但其實都看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.44,0:05:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都已經是第三次了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.76,0:06:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密碼做得相當好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.47,0:06:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媚月 哇...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.21,0:06:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.18,0:06:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!是我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.29,0:06:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是英司啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.13,0:06:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司?你在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.53,0:06:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媚月小姐 是我愛娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.40,0:06:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以打擾一下嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.78,0:06:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.98,0:06:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.08,0:07:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媚月小姐 發生什麼事了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.58,0:07:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳都溼透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.12,0:07:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊..我運動了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.55,0:07:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.06,0:07:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個..我在找英司少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.59,0:07:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有沒有到您這裡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.90,0:07:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司...沒在這裡呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.93,0:07:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他做了什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.50,0:07:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦\N只是想幫他檢查一下而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.04,0:07:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果又被他逃跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.61,0:07:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...我發現了就通知妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.34,0:07:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 抱歉打擾妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.11,0:07:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請您早點休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.78,0:07:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安 加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.02,0:07:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相當誘人的樣子耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.22,0:07:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝啦..我馬上就出去...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.59,0:07:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀~穿這樣偷跑到女生的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.37,0:07:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想就這麼走掉就算了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.23,0:07:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.70,0:07:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再多留一會兒嘛~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.88,0:08:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.75,0:08:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爺...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.52,0:08:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您在那裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.98,0:08:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爺...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.13,0:08:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇!好鬆喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.62,0:08:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要那麼緊張啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.96,0:08:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我..我哪有緊張...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.89,0:08:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是說...你是不是會錯意了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.13,0:08:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...我哪可能啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.90,0:09:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來還是第一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.77,0:09:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.11,0:09:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們倆單獨說話 請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.74,0:09:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個..這是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.48,0:09:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是果汁呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.31,0:09:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是讓你喝酒的話\N會被她罵死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.95,0:09:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.55,0:09:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.72,0:09:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道綾香跟我是朋友嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.93,0:09:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從來都沒聽說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.67,0:09:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我很早就想跟你說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.67,0:09:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我想在你\N有了心理準備之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.67,0:09:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是先保持沉默
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.57,0:09:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.94,0:09:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你實在是個大嘴巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.11,0:09:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼反正我就是口風不緊啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.55,0:09:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來陪陪我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.49,0:09:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據傳言說這座城裡的五個塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.79,0:10:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各自都藏有不同的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.36,0:10:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中一個\N就是綾香失去行蹤的西塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.73,0:10:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是那裡不是禁止進入的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.14,0:10:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我之前也曾打算偷偷的混進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.24,0:10:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後來被雷文罵到狗血淋頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.47,0:10:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怕了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.61,0:10:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別...別亂講!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.12,0:10:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到禁忌之塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.63,0:10:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來到這座城的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.63,0:10:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香已經在受訓中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.06,0:10:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接受你正在駕駛的G攻擊機的\N駕駛員訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.43,0:10:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香很適合成為一個飛行員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.74,0:10:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是因為G因子很少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.87,0:10:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法忍耐\N操縱超重機組的負荷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.44,0:10:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好像是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.18,0:10:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是她很認真對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.65,0:10:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勉強自己太過努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.18,0:10:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以還會打瞌睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.65,0:10:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真像她的作風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.65,0:10:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香就是那個時候消失的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.09,0:11:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時我因為有些事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.73,0:11:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以正好不在城裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.83,0:11:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.83,0:11:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個塔發生了事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.53,0:11:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說綾香就是被捲入那件事\N所以才消失的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.67,0:11:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事故?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.97,0:11:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算向女僕們及桑德曼詢問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.24,0:11:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都無法得知詳情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.64,0:11:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就等待\N來此調查的機會來臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.71,0:11:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後後來我終於成功的\N弄到通關密碼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.18,0:11:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是綾香消失的西塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.26,0:11:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是西塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.10,0:11:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.84,0:11:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是什麼地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.41,0:11:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡簡直...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.85,0:12:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們好像被關起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.29,0:12:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是不是也會消失呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.52,0:12:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像綾香那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.92,0:12:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.19,0:12:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.03,0:12:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.03,0:12:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.82,0:12:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.79,0:12:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是煙霧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.16,0:12:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.26,0:12:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.46,0:12:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡好像是\N跟重力有關係的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.67,0:12:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.07,0:12:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神也是依靠\N重力的能量來運作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.84,0:12:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正確的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.11,0:13:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從超重皇放出的重力子能量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.04,0:13:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在合神後的超重機組裡循環
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.65,0:13:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是就連機體也無法承受\N長時間的運作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.52,0:13:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐在上面的人也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.82,0:13:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G因子....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.22,0:13:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有對重力子的抵抗力\N就無法承受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.86,0:13:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像綾香...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.73,0:13:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,資料搜尋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.19,0:13:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再來就只要等待了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.13,0:13:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.60,0:13:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.67,0:13:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟愛很像呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.64,0:13:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.84,0:13:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力的真實面目\N到現在還不是很清楚哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.18,0:13:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但超重神\N是依靠重力能量運作的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.58,0:13:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才不可思議呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.12,0:13:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼\N已經查明重力的秘密了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.96,0:13:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個宇宙有四種力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.09,0:13:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依靠量子程度運作的有\N強的力量跟弱的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.26,0:13:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電磁力以及重力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.50,0:14:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他三種力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.07,0:14:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在現今物理學上都已獲得證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.47,0:14:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有重力\N至今依舊莫衷一是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.54,0:14:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管距離多遠\N重力都能夠運作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.01,0:14:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是種能讓彼此拉近距離\N使之結合的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.92,0:14:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像黑洞那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.45,0:14:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至連空間或時間\N都會遭到扭曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.62,0:14:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是它的真面目卻沒有人知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.93,0:14:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是種模糊不清又不可思議的能量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.53,0:14:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得這跟愛很像嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.13,0:14:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這對小孩子來說\N會不會太難了點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.10,0:14:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳...以前是幹什麼的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.41,0:14:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看來似乎\N對電腦跟科學的知識相當清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.81,0:14:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.02,0:14:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是綾香消失那天的影像紀錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.12,0:14:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡 是這個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.09,0:14:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西塔發生異常現象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.96,0:15:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保修班立刻前往\N將系統修復
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.60,0:15:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香小姐!不可以!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.47,0:15:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您的身體狀況還...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.24,0:15:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.05,0:15:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.29,0:15:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您在哪裡呢?綾香小姐...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.52,0:15:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到這就沒了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.29,0:15:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香從畫面消失之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.20,0:15:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到女僕們趕到為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.06,0:15:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅數秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.47,0:15:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真有點神秘耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.57,0:15:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.50,0:15:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生什麼事了，可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.21,0:15:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說...\N是從這邊掉下去...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.21,0:15:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什...什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.22,0:15:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個跟綾香消失的時候一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.93,0:16:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛...這到底是怎啦..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.37,0:16:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媚月!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.01,0:16:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.92,0:16:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.93,0:16:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.10,0:16:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開我 英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.97,0:16:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.50,0:16:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人要是做這種事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.97,0:16:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後一定會被綾香罵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.71,0:16:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候別耍酷 笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.45,0:16:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡不裝酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.95,0:17:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那要在哪裡裝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.10,0:17:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.34,0:17:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.97,0:17:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.02,0:17:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司...你醒了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.36,0:17:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.40,0:17:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不乖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.86,0:17:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老是做一些危險的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.53,0:17:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓姊姊擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.87,0:17:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.98,0:18:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.58,0:18:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你繼續駕駛超重神作戰的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.95,0:18:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們總有再見面的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.22,0:18:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛超重神作戰...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.59,0:18:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛超重神...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.46,0:18:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 駕駛超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.57,0:18:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎 綾香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.81,0:18:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.41,0:18:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司...總有一天...一定...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.08,0:18:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.25,0:18:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.52,0:18:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊姊姊\N哎呀...放開我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.66,0:18:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.06,0:18:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.53,0:18:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛...到底怎麼回事呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.27,0:19:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.14,0:19:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?哪裡?誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.41,0:19:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼哎呀呀啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.38,0:19:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然就抱著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.91,0:19:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.98,0:19:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?什麼?What?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.45,0:19:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個塔是禁止進入的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.82,0:19:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媚月應該也很清楚才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.85,0:19:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話\N希望你能盡量罰輕一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.92,0:19:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.29,0:19:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們...因為碰到地震
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.73,0:19:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後有一道奇怪的光\N就"碰"的冒了出來...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.10,0:19:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你們救了我們嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.47,0:19:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.87,0:19:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們進到這裡的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.64,0:19:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就看到兩位睡在這裡而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.07,0:19:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且也沒有什麼地震啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.74,0:19:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們完全沒有感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.24,0:19:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.91,0:19:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.45,0:19:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是有地震的話\N觀測班應該會發覺才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.02,0:19:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在也沒有報告進來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.75,0:19:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.29,0:19:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是作夢啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.29,0:19:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是媚月小姐也在場啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.90,0:20:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看應該再好好檢查一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.30,0:20:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次絕對不會讓你逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.60,0:20:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布麗姬妲 不要太急喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.87,0:20:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天一定可以再見面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.38,0:20:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.31,0:20:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有綾香觸感的餘溫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.52,0:20:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.88,0:20:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香果然還在某個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.69,0:20:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是綾香救了我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.96,0:20:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.69,0:20:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇怎麼流這麼多血啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.73,0:20:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也早點給我發現好不好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.76,0:20:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,檢查檢查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.60,0:20:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...手帕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.17,0:20:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔 謝啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.84,0:20:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.97,0:20:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血也流太多了吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.24,0:20:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,檢查檢查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.61,0:20:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.11,0:20:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈系統?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.88,0:20:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想把之前的事當做教訓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.55,0:20:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓超重神能夠\N即使沒有操控者也能運作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.75,0:20:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望能依據那個資料進行改造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.42,0:21:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是無人的自動機械\N豈不是違反了您的美學了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.43,0:21:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是可以的話\N我也不想派上用場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.76,0:21:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說只是緊急系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.34,0:21:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.44,0:21:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定不負您的期望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.31,0:21:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,努力開發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.79,0:21:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看著在烈陽熱氣下\N道路的那一方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.46,0:21:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,形形色色的事物\N呈現形形色色的擺動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.54,0:21:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知該為何這般\N心頭思緒紛亂不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.11,0:22:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但就這麼視而不見\N朝向明日飛去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.66,0:22:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為無法接受如此的不成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.79,0:22:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才說出了這麼不客氣的話語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.30,0:22:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若只是孤單一人地強出頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.14,0:22:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換來的只有誤解\N矛盾與迷惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.17,0:22:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於那牽繫著悲傷的羈絆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.24,0:22:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓微笑的雙眸中滲出了淚水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.85,0:22:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多想將這暖意傳送出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.45,0:22:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便緊握著手一直不願放開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.46,0:22:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好讓這祈禱得以傳達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.80,0:22:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪希露被外星異種抓去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.84,0:22:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求您 斗牙少爺\N請您救救雪希露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.64,0:22:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回播出 "龜裂"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.04,0:23:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下週\N我們也將照料各位的和平!